						<div class="postbody">For PocketNES, it was a big deal to work in bankable CHR-RAM or mappers with mixed CHR RAM and CHR ROM, mainly because of the way it uses the GBA hardware.  But other emulators with software renderers should have a much easier time.</div>

					
